title: Parallels Desktop Build 5600 + Windows XP Pro + serial
description:
Since I had some trouble finding a version of Parallels that \&#039;matched\&#039; with a Windows XP (had to try several combinations with different program- and OS versions and serials and yada yada before I managed to install), I decided to make this little package. These two in combination works perfectly fine.  

NOTE: 
This version of Parallels enables you to create Windows XP as a guest OS on your Mac (clearly, it will not work on your PC). Parallels will only work if your Mac has an Intel processor. If you\&#039;re unsure of the system requirements, check out parallels.com 

CONTENT:
Windows XP Pro
serials for the OS
Parallels Desktop Build 5600
serials for the program
